                </a>
                            <h3 class="promo-series__name">
            <span class="a11y">Series: </span>
            <span class="promo-series__title">Unplugged:</span>
                        <span class="promo-series__tagline">Will Taxpayers Foot the Oil Industry’s Cleanup Bill?</span>
                    </h3>
    </div>
    
        <a href="https://www.propublica.org/series/unplugged" class="promo-series__more-link">
        More in this series
        <div class="icon" style="transform: translateY(10%)">
            

