                    />

            
    
<figcaption class="attribution">
    
    
    
    </figcaption>

</figure>

        
    
                    
<p data-pp-blocktype="copy" data-pp-id="18.0">As you launch your business, begin by collecting subsidies, <a href="https://insideclimatenews.org/news/22102024/oil-company-government-payment-disclosures/">tax breaks</a> and other incentives from the government to guarantee you can pump oil and gas profitably. Globally, fossil fuel subsidies total in the trillions each year, <a href="https://www.imf.org/en/Blogs/Articles/2023/08/24/fossil-fuel-subsidies-surged-to-record-7-trillion">according to organizations such as the International Monetary Fund</a>.</p>
        
    
                    

<figure
    data-pp-id="19"
