<p data-pp-blocktype="copy" data-pp-id="22.0">As you set up your business, create layers of shell companies. Down the road, they’ll provide a firewall between you and your liabilities — key among them, cleanup costs.</p>
        
    
                    

<figure
    data-pp-id="23"
    data-pp-blocktype="image"
    class="bb-image size06 center  wide-sm wrap 
                ">

    


                    
    


