<p data-pp-blocktype="copy" data-pp-id="24.0">Once oil and gas production slows, sell low-producing wells. Smaller drillers operating on thinner margins, known in the business as “scavenger companies,” will be happy to take them off your hands.</p>
        
    
                    

<figure
    data-pp-id="25"
    data-pp-blocktype="image"
    class="bb-image size08 center  wide-sm wrap 
                ">

    


                    
    


